arts.ttl: Oyarzabal scores twice in first half to give Real Sociedad 2-1 win over Sevilla
arts.sum: A first-half double from captain Mikel Oyarzabal gave Real Sociedad a 2-1 win over Sevilla on Friday and lifted the Basque side out of the Spanish league relegation zone. Miscommunication from a throw-in between him and José Ángel Carmona gifted Sociedad the ball and Oyarzabal turned neatly inside the box and drilled a low drive under the Sevilla keeper.
Joe Champion has a correct score prediction for all of this weekend's round of ten fixtures in LaLiga, with games taking place across Friday, Saturday, Sunday and Monday.
